ne\/2015\/09\/01\/hasan-everyday-obey-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":0},"title":"Hasan on Eid: Every day Muslims obey Allah a celebration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 1, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Rajab reported: Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cEvery day in which Allah is not disobeyed is a celebration. Every day the believer spends in obedience, servitude, remembrance, and gratitude is a celebration.\u201d Source: Lat\u0323a\u0304'if al-Ma'a\u0304rif 1\/278 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0631\u062c\u0628 \u0642\u0627\u0644 \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0633\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0635\u0631\u064a \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u062a\u0639\u0627\u0644\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/15\/every-sinless-day-id\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":1},"title":"Hasan on Eid: Every day without sin is a celebration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Shawdhab reported: We were with Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, and he heard a man speaking during Eid. Al-Hasan said, \u201cEvery day in which Allah Almighty is not disobeyed is a celebration.\u201d Source: Musalsal al-\u02bb\u012adayn 28 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0634\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0630\u064e\u0628\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064f\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0639\u0650\u0646\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17189,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/13\/friday-eid-dress-nice-perfume\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Friday is an Eid, dress nice, wear perfume","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has made\u00a0this day of Friday a celebration\u00a0for the Muslims. Whoever comes to Friday prayer, let him bathe himself, apply perfume if he has it, and use the toothstick.\u201d Source: Sunan\u00a0Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1098 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36091,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/hasan-taqabbal-allahu-minna\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":3},"title":"Hasan on Eid: May Allah accept from us and from you","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Hawshab ibn \u2018Aqil reported: I met Al-Hasan al-Basri, may Allah have mercy on him, on the day of Eid and I said, \u201cMay Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Al-Hasan said, \u201cYes, may Allah accept good deeds from us and from you.\u201d Source: al-Du\u2019a\u0304\u2019 li-T\u0323abara\u0304ni 930 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5029,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/12\/sing-play-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Eid: Singing and playing on Eid","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came to my house when two girls were beside me singing songs of Bu\u2019ath. The Prophet laid down and turned his face to the other side. Then, Abu Bakr came in and spoke to me harshly, saying, \u201cMusical\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42529,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/02\/28\/prophets-grave-eid\/","url_meta":{"origin":36169,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Medina: Do not take Prophet\u2019s grave as celebration","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 28, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ali ibn al-Husayn reported: He saw a man coming to the opening by the grave of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he entered it to supplicate. \u2018Ali called for him and he said, \u201cShall I not narrate to you a tradition I heard from my father\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[